name: A Work of Art
description:
Front: 'a work of art'
Inside:'joyfully looking forward to welcoming your beautiful new 
   masterpiece!'
Back: 'Oh yes, you shaped me first inside, then out; You formed me
   in my mother's womb.  Thank you, HIgh God - you're breathtaking!  
   Body and soul, I am marvelously made!'    A quote by King David, this
   design celebrates the beauty of becoming a mother and inside and  
   out. Why not include a few picture frames with this card for the    
      'masterpiece' that is on its way!

name: Beautiful...Stunning...Radiant
description:
Outside: 'beautiful...stunning...radiant...'
Inside: '...that baby sure looks good on you!'

This hand painted watercolor celebrates the beauty of an expectant mother. Printed on feltweave paper, it comes with a heavy quality bright red envelope.  Add some bubble bath, or a basket of ways she can pamper herself and she will feel a like queen!

name: Wishing you....New Beginnings
description:
Outside: 'Wishing you a brand, spanking, fresh, shiny, unprecedented, 
    revolutionary...'
Inside:'...new beginning! the possibilities are endless...'
Back: 'Get started!'
Perfect for graduation, retirement, new job or even someone moving...rich and colorful, this card of encouragement adds an excitement to changes in someone's life.  The luxurious fern envelope adds an elegance to the feltweave design.  Send someone off with a new piece of luggage, diary or even a picnic basket full of yummy treats for their travels!

name: Welcome to the world sweet baby!
description:
Outside: 'welcome to the world sweet baby!
Inside: 'Your family already loves you more than you can imagine.'
The words say it all,don't you think?

name: Dream big
description:
'Dream big...' Inside: 'birthday girl!'

Hands on her hips and determined...Encourage the birthday girl, no matter how old she is, to keep those dreams alive.  Maybe you could give her a soft, plush pillow to help her on her way!

name: Hip Hip Hooray!
description:
Baby celebrations are the most fun!  Celebrate with this "Hip Hip Hooray!" cheer ...inside: "It's celebrate baby day!"   A card that can be given for a little boy or girl...perfect for that nursery with popular animal theme.

Felt weave, environmentally friendly quality paper adds an elegant touch to your gift!

name: Christmas 'Wishing you a merry...'
description:
Front: Have yourself a merry little Christmas...
Inside: Wishing you scrumptious serendepities during this sacred season!

Holidays...
Holiday fun and festivities captured on this group of watercolor designs reminds us of the joy of Christmas and the One we celebrate. These prints copied on beautiful environmental felt paper have the effect of an original watercolor.  Rich, high quality envelopes come with each card. May your Christmas holidays be filled with sweet serendipities sprinkled with quiet moments to celebrate Jesus' birth.

name: Antipication Pink
description:
"Anticipation"  says who will fill that inviting, whimsical stroller featured on the front.  This captures the excitement of the time of waiting for that new member of the family...and then the arrival. Inside: "Sweet celebration!" 

Available in pink or blue, it is perfect for that special shower gift or upon the arrival of that amazing little person. Felt weave, environmentally friendly quality paper adds an elegant touch to your gift.

name: Christmas 'Give Him the gift He really wants...'
description:
Front: Give Him the birthday gift He really wants this Christmas...
Inside: Your heart!

Holidays...
Holiday fun and festivities captured on this group of watercolor designs reminds us of the joy of Christmas and the One we celebrate. These prints copied on beautiful environmental felt paper have the effect of an original watercolor.  Rich, high quality envelopes come with each card. May your Christmas holidays be filled with sweet serendipities sprinkled with quiet moments to celebrate Jesus' birth.

name: Making a difference
description:
Front: Making a difference...
Inside: ...in the lives of those who know you. You are a gift!

Inspirations...
The Inspirational category of cards offer a variety of creative expressions...the colorful collection of pitchers created by Whitney Prueser represent an outpouring of love, hospitality and God's grace. The Pitcher series, as well as the layered piece, 'Guard your heart...' are on luxurious environmental felt paper and accompanied by quality jewel-toned envelopes.  
The collection of original photos, printed on a high quality cover stock paper, are of wonderful people, beautiful places and delicious moments captured from all over the world. We hope sharing these with you will help to encourage, comfort and inspire those you love!

name: Until one has loved an animal...
description:
Outside; "Until one has loved an animal...a part of one's soul remains unawakened."  A poignant quote by Anatole France, with the inside that reads: 'May cherished memories overshadow your loss.  We are thinking of you.'
Acknowledging  the loss of those wonderful pets who are part of the family means so much during this difficult time.

name: May the warmth of His love
description:
'May the warmth of His love flow through you... Inside: '...bringing joy to replace your sorrow.  Praying for you.'   Offering comfort during a difficult time, this is a gentle reminder that someone cares.  

Offered in a  5" x 7" size with a vibrant photo of leaves and light, this is created on heavy card stock paper.

name: All My Love
description: 'All my love....all my life.     'This elegant card is perfect for an anniversary, special celebration or simply left on a pillow or tucked in a briefcase as a lovely unexpected surprise.  Layered in handmade and gilded paper, mounted on a cream felt weave design, it becomes a gift in itself.  Add a special piece of jewelry or a romantic dinner to make an occasion unforgettable!

name: Pitcher A woman is like a teabag
description:
Front: A women is like a teabag...
Inside: you can’t tell how strong she is until you put her in
hot water. -Eleanor Roosevelt

Inspirations... 
The Inspirational category of cards offer a variety of creative expressions...the colorful collection of pitchers created by Whitney Prueser represent an outpouring of love, hospitality and God's grace. The Pitcher series, as well as the layered piece, 'Guard your heart...' are on luxurious environmental felt paper and accompanied by quality jewel-toned envelopes. 
The collection of original photos, printed on a high quality cover stock paper, are of wonderful people, beautiful places and delicious moments captured from all over the world. We hope sharing these with you will help to encourage, comfort and inspire those you love!

name: We got a great deal
description:
'We got a great deal on this party bus for your birthday.' Inside it says
'Just because we're cheap doesn't mean we love you less.'

Take a close look at that picture...that 'party bus' sure has lots of potential!  Created on heavy coverstock environmentally friendly paper...this card needs no gift.  Hey, cheap friends don't usually give a gift anyway!

name: Courage does not always roar
description:
"Courage does not always roar..."  Inside: "...sometimes it is the quiet voice at the end of the day that says, "I will try again tomorrow".   Hope."   The beautiful snow-covered mountain scene taken in the afternoon has several elements of symbolism that accompany this rich quote from M.A. Radmacher.  Give this as an expression of understanding and encouragement, turning perhaps fear or discouragement into hope, one day at a time.

An elegant size, 5" x 7", it is a card that will keep on encouraging that one you love.

name: Thanks Mom...
description:
Outside says 'Thanks, Mom...   Inside:  '...for loving me just the way I am.
                                                                     Love you back.'
Unconditional love...that's mom....and for that matter, it usually rings true for you favorite pet.  Add your own best memories of your past forgiven 'sins', just to let your mom know you still appreciate her grace.
Celebrate Mom all year!

name: You are a woman to be loved.
description:
Front: "You are a woman to be loved..."
Inside: "...and you are."
Back: "To love is to embrace life...risks and all"

Simple, elegant and eloquent!  Anniversaries, birthdays or even better, an unexpected sweet surprise...this greeting can be used for a variety of occasions.  Add a single stem of her favorite flower and the gift is complete.

Created from high quality, fsc (Forest Stewardship Council) approved felt-weave paper with a textured deckled edge.

name: Christmas 'Sunglasses, socks, mittens and ties'
description:
'Sunglasses, socks, mittens and ties...snuggles together, homemade cookies and pies...'  Inside: 'Wishing you exquisite moments as we celebrate Him with joy!'  

Make sweet memories out of simple joys this Christmas....delicious smells, snuggles, Christmas stories and songs of celebration for Him.  
Including a gift with this card?  How about a plate of cookies or a homemade pie? Yum.

name: Christmas Remember Him!
description:
Front: Remember the gifts? Remember friends? Remember family? Remember the food?
Inside: Remember Him?

Holidays...
Holiday fun and festivities captured on this group of watercolor designs reminds us of the joy of Christmas and the One we celebrate. These prints copied on beautiful environmental felt paper have the effect of an original watercolor.  Rich, high quality envelopes come with each card. May your Christmas holidays be filled with sweet serendipities sprinkled with quiet moments to celebrate Jesus' birth.

name: Embrace New Beginnings
description:
New leaf...new growth....original watercolor design..."Embrace new beginnings."  Inside: "Anticipate good things to come!"   A card for many occasions...a new year, a new job, retirement, significant life changes...have several on hand for that unexpected occasion.  

A rich, beautifullly textured card of environmentally friendly paper accompanied with a heavy quality, jewel-toned envelope.

name: Sylvia Plath Bath Quote
description:
Outside: There must be quite a few things that a hot bath won't cure, but I don't know may of them."
Inside: Blank

Layered papers create the feel of a luxurious bath just waiting to be enjoyed.  Enclose a envelope of bath salts and send to that friend that needs to be reminded to take time to relax! How about a gift bag with bath bubbles, a yummy smelling soap and some relaxing music as a birthday gift, thank you, or even a new house with the jacuzzi bath celebration.  The possibilities are endless!

Beautiful felt weave paper approved by the FSC (Forest Stewardship Council) indicates quality, as well as thought for the preservation of our forests.

name: Nobody knows the trouble
description:
Front: Nobody knows the trouble I’ve seen...
Inside: If you ever need a blues singer give me a call!

Inspirations...
The Inspirational category of cards offer a variety of creative expressions...the colorful collection of pitchers created by Whitney Prueser represent an outpouring of love, hospitality and God's grace. The Pitcher series, as well as the layered piece, 'Guard your heart...' are on luxurious environmental felt paper and accompanied by quality jewel-toned envelopes.  
The collection of original photos, printed on a high quality cover stock paper, are of wonderful people, beautiful places and delicious moments captured from all over the world. We hope sharing these with you will help to encourage, comfort and inspire those you love!

name: Father's Day 'You make even the ordinary...'
description:
Front: "You make even the ordinary fun..."
Inside: "Thanks for being a cool dad!"

We realize that not everyone has 'a cool dad', however we all know some cool dads!  It is time to celebrate those men who are making life sweeter for others in a very important way.  So here's to Bill Golden and all the other dad's who are making time and fun for their families... Let's celebrate them!

Colorful photo of real people in real life brought to you on heavy quality, fsc approved coverstock paper.

name: Shine!
description:
Outside: "The path of the righteous is like the morning sun, shining ever brighter...", "He who loves his brother abides in the Light..." and 
'You... you are the light..."you are the light of the world..." 
Bible verses on the front of this vibrant, watercolor that radiates to the back and says "...so that your Father in heaven may be glorified."
Inside: 'He's shining through you!'

This lovely felt weave design could be use for birthdays, anniversaries or a thank you for someone who has radiate His light in your life. This card is accompanied with a rich golden envelope.

name: You make me feel like a puppy again...
description:
Outside: 'You make me feel like a puppy again...'
Inside: 'frisky.'
Light-hearted and fun, this little card shows one of our favorite 
four-legged friends, Lotus, who definitely knows the meaning of the word 'frisky'! With a twinkle in your eye, use this to do a little flirting...even if you have been married for years!

name: Mama's Hands
description:
Front: 'loving. serving. holding. encouraging. praying. wiping tears...'
       Inside: 'Your hands are beautiful.  Thank you, mama.'

A sentiment from the heart...hands that reflect the loving that went into life as a mother.  That's my 'mama'!  Maybe it's your's too. 
Maybe this lovely cream colored card and envelope should come with a tissue!

name: Mother
description:
Front: 'Mother...the holiest calling of God heard on the lips and hearts of children.'        Inside: 'Happy day to a beautiful mother!'
           Back: "Her children rise up and call her blessed." Proverbs 31:28

A Cutie and Noodle original watercolor of soft red hearts, surrounded by flowers and vines, is a perfect card for your own mother, or perhaps for someone who has been like a mother to you.  A lovely bouquet of spring flowers completes this gift to make any mom feel special!

 printed on environmentally friendly feltweave paper. This card is accompanied by a lovely coverstock cream card.

name: Every leaf a miracle
description:
Front: "Every leaf a miracle." Walt Whitman
Inside: "May we enjoy His abundance with gratitude...Happy Thanksgiving!"

name: Sweater
description:
Outside: 'sweater,n.: garment worn by child when mother is feeling chilly'
Inside:'thanks for keeping me warm. mom, I love you.'
Can anyone relate to this poignant sentiment?  Layered-up for the cold weather to the point you can barely move?  It was just mom loving us extra hard.  This could bring a smile to your mother's face...include a cuddly couch 'throw' or blanket, and you have the perfect gift!

name: Olive you, Mom
description:
'Olive you, Mom', a new addition to the 'Olive' series, is perfect for any occasion...How about Mother's Day?  Blank in the middle, this card gives you the opportunity to share your precious words that are gifts to her. If she is an olive-lover, a basket full of assorted jars of olives, fun napkins and if you can find the olive candy (chocolate that looks like an olive with an almond in the middle...delish!) definitely make it an addition.  Oh, and did anyone say martini??

Assembled with care in three layers, with luxurious handmade red paper on an environmentally-friendly felt weave textured background card.  A gift in itself!

name: Yep, it's your birthday again.
description:
Outside: 'Yep, it's your birthday again.'
Inside: 'Roll in something good.'
Who's happier than a dog who has just relished a moment of sheer delight? The perfect card to encourage a friend to have their own perfect day!

name: Sunflowers "People from a planet without flowers..."
description:
Gardeners and flower-lovers everywhere should relate to this quote from Iris Murdoch..."People from a planet without flowers must think we are mad with joy the whole time to have such things about us."  Inside reads 'Like the beauty that surrounds us, you bring joy!'  

Sunflowers array the front of this original watercolor, with the little reminder on the back...'Give thanks to the Giver' comes with a rich rust envelope.  Enclose a pack of seeds to mail, or gather a natural bouquet from your garden and surprise someone special with a personal delivery.  Spread the joy!

name: Stay Strong
description:
Front: Stay strong.
Inside: “Be of good courage and
He shall strengthen your heart...” Psalms 27:14

Inspirations...
The Inspirational category of cards offer a variety of creative expressions...the colorful collection of pitchers created by Whitney Prueser represent an outpouring of love, hospitality and God's grace. The Pitcher series, as well as the layered piece, 'Guard your heart...' are on luxurious environmental felt paper and accompanied by quality jewel-toned envelopes.  
The collection of original photos, printed on a high quality cover stock paper, are of wonderful people, beautiful places and delicious moments captured from all over the world. We hope sharing these with you will help to encourage, comfort and inspire those you love!

name: A Kiss Is A Rosy Dot
description: Who gives you the best kisses? Maybe it's that grandchild who sprinkles the sweetest little 'rosy dots' all over your cheeks...or a friend who likes to greet you the European way...a kiss on each cheek.  This great little quote by Cerano de Bergerac, "A kiss is a rosy dot over the 'i' of loving.", is not just for those romantic times, with the inside saying 'May I please have an exclusive serving of your delicious rosy dots?'  The back of the card is just as fun...'...more kisses please.' with a watercolor of an empty bowl.  Accompany with just a few chocolate kisses and it is sure to bring a smile!

name: The Lord bless you
description:
"The Lord bless you and keep you, the Lord make His face to shine upon 
   you" On the back "...and give you peace." Numbers 6:24-25
            Inside: 'Celebrating you on your special day!'
This could celebrate good health news, a remarkable accomplishment, adoption date or birthday... those special wishes could hardly be any better.  Guess who that is leaping for joy...possibly someone who is sometimes called 'Noodle'?

name: I can't help it
description: They say that dogs are a man's best friend...they will greet you anytime of the day or night with that  welcoming, wagging tail that can be out of control. What a fun card to slip into your spouse's suitcase when they leave for a business trip, or a just a fun reminder that you love coffee or tea time with your dog-loving friend.  'I can't help it...' on the front, inside '...my tail starts to wag when I hear you coming.'  Have any visitors planning a visit?  A perfect card for setting the stage for a fun event!

name: Our Lord Has Written
description: This simple felt weave design contains a quote from Martin Luther..."Our Lord has written the promise of the resurrection, not in books alone, but in every leaf in springtime."  Inside: 'Rejoice.'  The back contains a watercolor of a tree branch bursting with new growth and the quote from John 11:25, "I am the resurrection and the life." This card is accompanied with a bright red high quality envelope that compliments the little red bird on the front. Enjoy your spring and may it remind you of sacred things!

name: Do not abandon yourselves to despair...
description:
"Do not abandon yourselves to despair...
Inside: ...we are the Easter people and hallelujah is our song."
This quote by Pope John Paul II sums up this season of celebration in a beautiful and inspiring way... with this photo taken in Italy, no less.
Bring a bouquet of sunflowers to the Easter feast, and memories will continue long after the day has passed.

name: Behold, I make all things
description: The beautiful, hopeful verse, "Behold, I make all things new."  found in Revelations 21:5 is accompanied with sunshine and a burst of flowers sets the stage for the inside text: 'another chance. a new beginning. fresh hope.  God's grace everyday.'  This could be a card of encouragement, new beginnings or a celebration of Easter.  The back has a little framed flower with 'Thank you God.' included.  Designed on lovely felt weave paper that comes with an elegant forest green card stock envelope. A card handy to have for those unexpected occasions.

name: Most precious possession
description:
Outside: "The most precious possession that ever comes to a man in this world is a woman's heart." A quote by Josiah Holland, with the inside that simply says 'I love your heart.'
A perfect card for an anniversary, birthday, or 'just because'... sometimes words are the best gift you can give the woman you love.

name: If you live to be a hundred
description:
Front: "If you live to be a hundred, I want to live to be a hundred minus 
     one day...
Inside: ...so I never have to live without you."  A timeless quote by 
    A.A. Milne, this is perfect for a birthday, anniversary, Valentines Day
    ...or just because you want your special person to know how much 
    they are loved.

name: Olive you for always
description: Fun, whimsical cards made of high quality environmental water color paper created in three layers and made with love!

name: Love...you!
description: Irresistable hearts..."Love...you!"  simple, but fun...for your pal or your your honey, this can be a card for many occasions.  Anniversary?  Birthday? Thank you?  Mom?  Dad?  This A7, heavy quality card comes with a bright red, luxurious envelope to match.  All you need is a hug to go with it!

name: "I Love You Lots..."
description:
Fun, whimsical little card..."I love you lots, even more than flower pots, tater tots, polka dots, robots..."  Inside: Happy birthday to yousie!"

Presented on heavy card stock environmentally friendly paper, with a bright green, distinct envelope...this makes a fun card for your honey, friend or family member.

name: Olive your Heart
description:
'Olive your heart' is the perfect new card from the 'Olive' series that can be given to a family member or friend for Valentine's Day, as a 'thank you' or just as an observation that they have one of the biggest hearts you know!   It is nice to be noticed...add a sweet note of encouragement and you have just made their day!

Assembled with care in three layers, with luxurious handmade red paper on an environmentally-friendly felt weave textured background card.  A gift in itself!

name: Chicky Cheek Pecks
description:
Outside: "Chicky cheek pecks"
Inside a choice of: "...Happy birthday from your peeps!"
                                                or
                              " ...muah!...muah! muah!"
(Indicate preference under 'special instructions' in your order.)

Light, airy and fun...a way to celebrate a birthday, or even the perfect little card for any occasion with ('muah' ) kisses enclosed.

A layered attachment on environmentally-conscious (fsc approved) felt weave paper.

name: Olive you a bushel and a peck
description:
Fun, whimsical cards made of high quality environmental water color paper created in three layers and made with love!

And, of course, the inside says...' and a hug around the neck!'

name: Party Bus
description:
Does this Volkswagen picture jar any memories for you? Good for all occasions, on the front 'Your party bus is here!' and inside, 'Ride on.'   Whether for a birthday, congratulations or just plain 'let's get out of here!' message have a few of these on hand for a variety of occasions. 
Oh, and did we mention the 'Peace out' sign on the back? Far out.

name: Begin to weave...
description: Beautiful layers of fibers and fabrics embellish this card to create a one-of-a-kind piece of art. Each card, created by hand, has  an array of rich textures that form a vibrant collage of three-dimensional color.  As pieces of fiber are applied with love, it is fun to imagine the recipient of each of these uniquely designed cards.  Share this elegant little gift with those most special in your life!

name: Luke
description:
Know any dog-lovers? Inside: 'I really like you.'  You could send this to someone you secretly admire, just want to cheer up or someone you want to thank for being so nice.  Spread the love!

By the way,  this pooch's name is Luke and he will give you a juicy kiss when you least expect it!

name: American Flag
description: "True heroism is remarkably sober, very undramatic...it is not the urge to surpass all others at whatever the cost, but the urge to serve others at whatever the cost."   A quote by arthur ashe, here's a way to show gratitude to those in service to our country now or in the past, as well as the families of these heroes.  As we know, freedom comes at a price... with the inside that reads a simple 'Thank you.' let us take a moment to support our heroes in America.  If it's not enough, add a check to the Fisher House or Wounded Warriors, or another organization helping soldiers and families. Cutie and Noodle did!

name: It's only a birthday
description:
Front: It’s only a birthday.
Inside: Buck up and have fun!

Celebrations:
This selection of cards offer a variety of art....photos from all over the world capturing wonderful people and exquisite places, joined by fun artwork full of whimsical characters, both  selections printed on high quality cover stock paper. Included, as well, in the Celebrations category are vibrant watercolors printed on beautiful textured environmental felt paper of the finest quality. Make everyday a celebration!

name: Drenched in God
description:
You can almost touch the dew on this beautiful cluster of berries...'We live in a world drenched in God.' is certainly illustrated here.  Inside: 'So glad He created you.  Happy birthday!'
A reminder that family and friends are one of the most sacred creations from God. .. may we celebrate each other, as well as Him!

This 5" x 7" card made from heavy card stock is a gift in itself!

name: You are a treasure...
description:
Simple, elegant and meaningful....this card is layered with handmade paper and fibers...some pieces may have been found on the North Sea beach along the coast of Denmark.  Turn the deckled edge to peek inside...the message reads 'Priceless.'  Individually created, no two cards are exactly alike. The back has a pastel watercolor bloom with the simple word, 'Cherished'.  Not a card for everyone in your life...just a very special few.

True for all of our cards, the paper used is FSC approved...using trees that are harvested with the preservation of our environment in mind.

name: Your heart in His hand
description:
'Your heart in His hand...' , inside: 'Wishing you His peace.'
Elegant, handmade paper, layered in rich colors...a simple, heartfelt message of encouragement for someone who has lost a loved one, has an illness, or just needs to know they are loved.  

Accompanied with a rich, brick-colored envelope...a good card to have on hand for those unexpected times in life.

name: Take really deep breaths
description:
Colorful, whimsical...'Take really deep breaths. Smack your lips! Relish the day.'   Inside: 'It's yours.  Have a yummy birthday!'  This card makes it easy to find the perfect gift...chocolate candy? a trip to the yogurt shop and the bar full of toppings? a day of drive-thrus or a fancy dinner? Birthday indulgence is permitted!  

This card comes with a bright 'Cheeto colored' envelope...hey, did someone say Cheetos?  m-m-m...now you're talking!

name: Grace
description:
Colorful Easter blessings in a  sunflower adorned 'Grace' on the outside with the inside greeting 'that taught my heart to sing...amazing  Grace.
Easter joy to you!'  The back continues the theme with the Psalm 30:11 verse that says "You turned my wailing into dancing; you removed my sackcloth and clothed me with joy!"  

Another Cutie and Noodle original watercolor printed on luxurious feltweave, environmentally friendly paper accompanied by a high quality tomato-red envelope.

name: May God hold you close
description:
Serene image from the Czech Republic, 'May God hold you close.'
Inside, 'Praying for you.'  Simple, comforting and heartfelt, a card for many occasions...so many people today need a word of encouragement.
Few words say it all.

name: Kiss me
description:
'"Kiss me with the kisses of your mouth...' an elegant, sensual card in soft pastels. Inside, completes this verse from Song of Solomon, '"...for your love is sweeter than wine."'

The back, "Where should one put perfume?", the young woman asked. "Wherever one wants to be kissed." she replied.  With her famous array of perfumes, who else but Coco Chanel!

Enclosed in a beautiful envelope, Valentines or anniversary...or a sweet surprise out of the blue...keep the romance alive!

name: Whee!
description: Can you almost hear the squeals of laughter?  'Whee' on the front and the inside says 'Hope your birthday is as fun YOU!'  Sprinkle some confetti in the envelope and send a smile to one the most fun people in your life.  Take it to a birthday party with some tootie horns and a party hat, and heck, maybe even a whoopee cushion. Fun should be an essential ingredient in just about everyday, don't you think?

name: Thank you, God.
description: 'Thank you, God.' with a face of gratitude in sepia tones includes the inside message 'Grateful for you.'.   Sometimes just a simple card is best when you don't have words to express your appreciation.  Fill this year with gratitude for family, friends and those who may be surprised to know they are appreciated. Don't they say...'a thankful heart is a happy heart' ?

name: Women of Wonder
description:
Women of Wonder celebrating life...whirling scarves, fancy hats, dancing in the rain with the inside that reminds us to 'laugh. jubilate. cultivate. love. moment to moment. live vibrantly. live simply. enjoy the dance.' A reminder to  'be you and enjoy it.' completes the back of this greeting.

Handy for special birthdays, congratulations, encouragement, or just a reminder to friends of just how wonderful they are... accompanied by a colorful scarf, lively umbrella, wild hat or vase of daisies you have a perfect gift!

name: Sophie
description:
'Sophie refused to blink for fear of missing one moment of her birthday.' Inside: 'Have a wide-eyed wonderful day!'

Know someone who needs a little birthday cheer...no matter how old they are?!  Give them Sophie, a smile and maybe even a bag full of silly fun...how about some jacks, some pick up sticks, bubbles and gum.  Celebrate silly. Celebrate like a kid. Giggles anyone?

name: Yearbook Fashionista
description:
Front: Yearbook Fashionista
Inside: ...that’s you... always making a statement. Happy birthday to an outstanding friend!

Celebrations: 
This selection of cards offer a variety of art....photos from all over the world capturing wonderful people and exquisite places, joined by fun artwork full of whimsical characters, both selections printed on high quality cover stock paper. Included, as well, in the Celebrations category are vibrant watercolors printed on beautiful textured environmental felt paper of the finest quality. Make everyday a celebration!

name: It takes courage (red berry)
description:
Front: It takes courage to grow up and become who you really are." e.e.cummings
Two versions inside...
    'Happy birthday to brave and wonderful you!' or
    Celebrate you.' (this second version includes the back with another 
    e.e. cummings quote, "To be nobody but yourself in a world which is
    doing its best, night and day, to make you everybody else means to 
    fight the hardest battle which any human being can fight...and never  
    stop fighting."  
    Indicate which version you prefer when ordering

Celebrations:
This selection of cards offer a variety of art....photos from all over the world capturing wonderful people and exquisite places, joined by fun artwork full of whimsical characters, both  selections printed on high quality cover stock paper. Included, as well, in the Celebrations category are vibrant watercolors printed on beautiful textured environmental felt paper of the finest quality. Make everyday a celebration!

name: Trust steadily in God (pink hearts)
description:
Beautiful handpainted design..."Trust steadily in God...hope unswervingly...love extravagantly..."  Inside:"...and the best is Love!"  The love theme continues on the back with "...meditate on things true, noble, reputable, authentic, compelling, gracious...the best...the beautiful...thing to praise...and God will work you into His most excellent harmonies."  These excerpts taken from 1 Corinthians 13 and Philippians 4.  

Perfect for weddings, anniversaries and Valentine's Day, this card is a gift in itself!  Printed on rich , textured environmentally friendly paper, enclosed in a beautiful cream card stock envelope.

name: Olive our life
description: Fun, whimsical cards made of high quality environmental water color paper created in three layers and made with love!

name: Olive the beach!
description:
'Olive the beach!' new to the 'Olive' series makes you want to grab a good book, pack a little lunch and head to the water!  This decked out olive could be used for an invitation, appreciation or along with a gift that says 'it's time to relax!'.

Felt weave, environmentally friendly quality paper adds an elegant touch to make this a gift in itself.

name: Olive you, Daughter
description:
'Olive you, Daughter' dedicated to my daughter, (I love you, Whitney!), is a new addition to the 'Olive series'.  Blank on the inside, this card can be given for any occasion...Valentine's Day, birthday, thank you...the list goes on.  Never underestimate the power of words and the importance of expressing your love and appreciation.

Three layers to this handmade card, make it a apecial gift in itself. Add a little gift card to share time over coffee or shopping...wow!

name: Relax
description:
Outside: "Relax"
Inside: "It's your birthday!"
                       or
             "Reflect. Renew. Rejoice!"
 (Indicate your choice of inside text under 'special instructions' in   
       your order.)

Imagine soaking in a flower-covered bathtub filled with bubbles, in cozy surroundings reading a delicous book...what could be more inviting?  A little paper back and this card makes a perfect gift for anybody who even likes the idea of a bath!

Bright, yellow background with a whimsical piece of art attached to environmentally friendly felt weave paper makes a little gift in itself!

name: Wanda
description:
Front: Wanda, far left, thinks this birthday you should act your age...
Inside: ...forget Wanda...party down.

Celebrations:
This selection of cards offer a variety of art....photos from all over the world capturing wonderful people and exquisite places, joined by fun artwork full of whimsical characters, both  selections printed on high quality cover stock paper. Included, as well, in the Celebrations category are vibrant watercolors printed on beautiful textured environmental felt paper of the finest quality. Make everyday a celebration!

name: Anticipation Yellow
description:
"Anticipation"  says who will fill that inviting, whimsical stroller featured on the front. This card is blank inside, and could be used to accompany a gift or gift card, or as a 'thank you' note for the parents-to-be.

Colorful in yellow and blue, this a card is perfect for a little boy or girl. Felt weave, environmentally friendly quality paper adds an elegant touch to your gift or thank you!

Special pricing for a pack of eight available too.

name: Home Sweet Home
description:
'Home Sweet Home' is an elegant little layered card that could be used as a 'thank you' for hospitality, for someone returning home from the military, or even a vacation, or someone who has just moved into a new home.  Know any realtors or travel agents looking for an edge on their competition?  Blank inside, this little treasure can be handy for a variety of occasions.

Made of environmentally-friendly felt weave paper, accompanied with an elegant, cover weight envelope, this card is a gift in itself!

name: Olive All of You
description:
'Olive all of you', new  to the series, makes a perfect Valentine or anniversary card for your main squeeze...especially when you can't find the perfect card with just the right words. Inside is blank so add your own expression...or hey, even some poetry.  Get creative.  Who knows what might develop!

Assembled with care in three layers, with luxurious handmade red paper on an environmentally-friendly felt weave textured background card.

name: Friends forever
description:
Front: Friends forever.
Inside: Happy birthday, dear friend.

Celebrations:
February is a great month for fabulous birthdays!  In celebration of a very special friendship that represents many, may we all treasure those we hold close with love and affection, and those who have touched us in some way... you know who you are! Happy birthday, Beth...this picture taken by my mother...who always had her camera ready. May we all make everyday a celebration!

We use high quality cover stock paper for our designs, because you are worth it, as so are we!

name: Olive to Celebrate!
description:
Fun, whimsical cards made of high quality environmental felt weave paper created in three layers and made with love! What occasions could this be used for...let me count the ways...party invitation, birthday, anniversary, Christmas, Ground Hog Day, new job, a promotion, a raise, a really good grade...the list is endless!

Our philosophy at Cutie and Noodle is find something to celebrate everyday...you want to join us?
